{"tid":223052,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"平心而論 拆彈專家其實幾好睇","createTime":"2017-04-30T04:59:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T06:01:50.000Z","uid":76804,"like":34,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d193d65237ce5d6b86906f5b4bb53396753292b6","tid":223052,"uid":76804,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T04:59:28.000Z","msg":"港產片黎講大製作拍到咁精品其實幾難得<br />\n好多位睇得出好認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拆彈真係有做功課 條隧道真係1:1做出黎<br />\n拆彈機械人原來都係道具黎<br />\n<br />\n套戲有好多香港景 好有親切感<br />\n愛情位盡量濃縮 但又配合到情節 滿足下d女觀眾<br />\n又拍得好緊張 特技好真<br />\n好過寒戰果種扮曬野 又成日ending留伏線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢d香港大製作買少見少 難得劉華肯投資 係合拍片情況下盡量保留港產味<br />\n套戲都用左好多香港綠葉 babyjohn都交到戲 黑仔好搞笑<br />\n唔明點解d打住本土旗號 但拍到舊屎咁 都咁多人追捧<br />\n但呢套咁認真製作 就比人話垃圾 浪費生命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15764ad4e3783ee9698c9500461abc9e6f8edc15","tid":223052,"uid":84228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T05:14:39.000Z","msg":"比起寒戰，拆彈專家更拍得似大片"},{"pid":"a8f5a1e665699ccb3d25fd3f76e2560799c7bc91","tid":223052,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T07:52:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比起寒戰，拆彈專家更拍得似大片</blockquote><br />\n寒戰個格局係細好多<br />\n講權鬥都係好片面"},{"pid":"7ba6d1a3af29595967579caed8ed04e1ef26d70a","tid":223052,"uid":33439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T08:00:08.000Z","msg":"入面D劇情奴性重到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9777506ae28bdb7bc23079f11b60a2cda3e649b","tid":223052,"uid":112165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:16:21.000Z","msg":"真係好好睇 完全冇冷場<br />\n好似好快睇完咁 好緊張刺激<br />\n估唔到有少少笑位"},{"pid":"5e55b3cfc72051e61b44aa76164408e02ce5ace8","tid":223052,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T09:31:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入面D劇情奴性重到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor